# Project-private path blocklist -- TEMPLATE
#
# Copy this file to "private-paths.local" in the same folder:
#
#   cp .githooks/private-paths.local.example .githooks/private-paths.local
#
# Then list one path substring per line. The pre-commit hook blocks any
# staged file whose path contains a listed substring. '#' starts a comment.
#
# private-paths.local is gitignored, so its contents stay on your machine
# and never reach this PUBLIC repo.
#
# Example entries (replace with your own):
#   internal-notes/
#   private-docs/
#   client-data/
